    "This is caused by the mapping applied to the outliers.",
    "To mitigate this issue, we train a transformer encoder classifier on the training set using the labels obtained from the unsupervised topic modelling but excluding the outliers.",
    "This improves the accuracy score to ca. 80%.",
    "To conclude, unsupervised topic modelling provides an easy approach in the absence of sufficient labelled text data.",
